<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/291549-i-have-heard-so-many-great-things-about">I have heard so many great things about this novel and it&#39;s second half Judas Unchained, but I keep starting it, getting 200-300 pages into it and get really bogged down; too many characters, kind of boring, should I plow through or have others had a similar experience. Does the novel blossom after page say 400?</a>
</div>
