<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/56778880-gerard">Gerard</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Ditch it immediately! Don&apos;t waste another minute on this overblown, badly written nonsense.<br/>My god it was a terribly long march to the end and it just <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Ditch it immediately! Don't waste another minute on this overblown, badly written nonsense.<br />My god it was a terribly long march to the end and it just got worse page by page. There were whole plot lines that went nowhere and characters who did nothing and added less.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
