  <span id="freeText10064985521113010058" style="display:none"><b>Superb, Awesome! The first-half of The Commonwealth Saga is 988 pages. The second half "Judas Unchained" is 1,236 pages and completes the "2,200 page single book". Don't be scared off! This is an incredible value!</b><br /><br />This is Very Good, hard sci-fi, many many characters, so it takes a while to get into the book. When I started the first book, I felt there were far too many, too wordy descriptions of the local scene. Creative often, but perhaps the whole saga could lose 100 pages.<br /><br />The evolution of the aggressive alien species is truly Brilliant.<br /><br />See rest of review in Judas Unchained.</span>
