<span id="freeTextContainer8743669075443871934">Peter F. Hamilton is a British science fiction author. He is best known for writing space opera. As of the publication of his tenth novel in 2004, his works had sold over two million copies worldwide, making him Britain&apos;s biggest-selling science fiction author.</span>
  <span id="freeText8743669075443871934" style="display:none">Peter F. Hamilton is a British science fiction author. He is best known for writing space opera. As of the publication of his tenth novel in 2004, his works had sold over two million copies worldwide, making him Britain's biggest-selling science fiction author.</span>
